             was indicted for <rs id="t18251027-190-off1091" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18251027-190-off1091" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18251027-190-off1091" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18251027-190-cd1092" type="crimeDate">25th of September</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18251027-190-off1091 t18251027-190-cd1092"></join>, a hat, value 2 s., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18251027-190-victim1024" type="victimName">
                        William 
                        Hamilton
                     <interp inst="t18251027-190-victim1024" type="surname" value="Hamilton"></interp>
